            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>eo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>In</abbr><ex>victo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>ithrae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex cert="low">acrum</ex></expan> pro <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>alute</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustorum!</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostrorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sep</abbr><ex>timii</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Valerius et Valerianus <expan><abbr>sex</abbr><ex>viri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>arnunti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mithrasrelief mit separat gearbeiteter Basis; Z. 1-3 auf der Basis, Z. 4 auf dem Stiernacken. Z. 1: S(oli)? Im Relief noch Reste eines Stucküberzugs und von Farbe. Z. 4: Schreibtechnik: Graffito. (B): CIMRM 1659: Z. 1: I(nvicto); Krüger: Z. 4: nicht angegeben.</p>
            </div>
